title: Netflix (NFLX) Up or Down on October 30?
description:

This market will resolve to "Down" if the official NASDAQ closing price for Netflix, Inc. (NFLX) on Thursday, October 30, 2025 is lower than the official NASDAQ closing price for NFLX on the most recent prior trading day.
